Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before transitioning to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of all 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' activities within a case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to 'Accepted + In Progress' across cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to 'Completed + Resolved' for all instances
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Duration comparison between 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' for completing subsequent activity

Name: Average time it takes to resolve a case after 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' is performed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Duration from the first occurrence of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to the last activity in the case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases involving 'Org line A2'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' without transitioning to another activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x0000029E3FC4F910> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Total time cases spend in 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before being escalated
